- What are you doing?
- Master Fugui.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_22

segmentosSRT.text: Here, bite on this. It'll save your teeth.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_22

segmentosSRT.text:
Fengxia! You'll pull through.
Mommy's here. Don't be afraid.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_22

segmentosSRT.text: Please, Doctor, she's my only daughter.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_22

segmentosSRT.text: The only child I have left.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_22
